text: The Jönköping Pentecostal Church () is a church building in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It belongs to the Swedish Pentecostal Movement. Che current church is located near the Western Square. It was inaugurated on 1 February 1981. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Churches in Sweden Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping
